- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper proposes a method to diagnose cases when the proposed invariant is not inductive. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of SMT solvers, which are commonly used in AI applications. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is relevant as the paper deals with the verification of invariants, which is a topic in formal methods.
